			<style>/*! elementor - v3.19.0 - 28-02-2024 */
.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}</style>				<div id="content" class="site-content"><div class="ast-container"><div id="primary" class="content-area primary"><p> </p><article id="post-556" class="post-556 page type-page status-publish ast-article-single"><div class="entry-content clear"><div class="elementor elementor-556" data-elementor-type="wp-page" data-elementor-id="556"><section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7993104 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="7993104" data-element_type="section" data-settings="{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}"><div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default"><div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-74acc20" data-id="74acc20" data-element_type="column"><div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-43d2c89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="43d2c89" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h2><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>Terms and conditions</b></span></h2><p> </p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>1. Objectives</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">It is the goal of {{ get_settings('website_name')}} (“{{ get_settings('website_name')}}”), to help users enter and navigate the cryptocurrency space, and provide tools to help users make their own sound decisions relative to growing their wealth. Services are intended for medium- and long-term investors.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>2. Activities</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">2.1 Account creation</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} will create the necessary crypto exchange accounts on behalf of, and with permission of the user. Once account set-up is complete, users are provided with the account credentials and password change instructions, at which point users will have full control over their account. Users are the full and sole owner of their exchange accounts and carry all responsibilities that come with opening, holding, and managing such accounts.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">2.2 Asset allocation</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} uses dynamic, proprietary algorithms to define and perform portfolio allocation, based on user input. Manual trades or transactions conducted by users may limit {{ get_settings('website_name')}}’s account monitoring and reporting ability.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">2.3 Fund deposits and withdrawals</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">Users are responsible for depositing and withdrawing funds to/from their account, however {{ get_settings('website_name')}} will provide clear instructions on how to do so.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">2.4 Account monitoring and reporting</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} will continuously monitor user accounts and provide users with a monthly dashboard with easy-to-understand portfolio and performance details.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>3. Fees</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">3.1 Fee structure</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} offers different plans: freemium, and performance fee. The freemium plan is totally free and offers limited functionality.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">Our customers especially like the no-profit-no-pay model as it means that {{ get_settings('website_name')}} only gets paid if the customer wins. We like this also!</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">3.2 Promotions</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} reserves the right to apply promotional discounts to the fees listed under 3.1. This is completely at {{ get_settings('website_name')}}’s discretion.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">3.3 Other fees</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} does not charge any additional or hidden fees. For any transaction or trading fees that may be charged by cryptocurrency exchanges and/or banks, users accept full responsibility.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>4. Security</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">4.1 Infrastructure</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} is powered by Google Cloud. Google Cloud helps reducing the cost, complexity, and risk associated with security and compliance in the cloud.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">4.2 Exchanges</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} thoroughly vets its partners and only works with major “top-10” exchanges. User funds remain on their personal exchange account and interactions between {{ get_settings('website_name')}} and user accounts are performed by means of customer owned API keys. API access is limited, hence in the unlikely event of a security breach, no fund withdrawal can take place.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>5. Disclaimer</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">5.1 Financial advice</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} does not provide financial advice. {{ get_settings('website_name')}} is not a Registered Investment Advisor, Broker/Dealer, Financial Analyst, Bank, Securities Broker, Commodity Trade Advisor, or Financial Planner. The information provided, such as optimal fund allocation, is based on user input and for information purposes only. The Information is not intended to be and does not constitute financial advice or any other advice, is general in nature and not specific to you. Before using {{ get_settings('website_name')}}, users should seek the advice of a qualified investment professional and undertake their own due diligence. {{ get_settings('website_name')}} is not responsible for any investment decision made by users.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">5.2 Warranties</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} disclaims to the full extent authorized by law any and all warranties, whether express or implied, including, without limitation, any implied warranties, merchantability or fitness for a particular purpose. {{ get_settings('website_name')}} does not warrant that its services and applications will be free of bugs, errors, viruses or other defects, nor that trade results will be profitable.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">5.3 Liability</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">In no event can {{ get_settings('website_name')}} or any of its owners be liable to users or any party related to users for any indirect, incidental, consequential, special, exemplary, or punitive damages, lost profits, or losses, even if {{ get_settings('website_name')}} has been advised of the possibility of such damages. In any event, {{ get_settings('website_name')}}’s total aggregate liability to users for all damages of every kind and type (regardless of whether based in contract or tort) shall not exceed the fees paid to {{ get_settings('website_name')}} for the use of our services or applications.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>6. Risks</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">Investing in any asset class, including crypto currencies, holds numerous risks, for example: technology risks, exchange risks, security risks, regulatory risks.  Before deciding to leverage {{ get_settings('website_name')}} services, users should carefully consider their investment objectives and risk appetite. The possibility exists that users lose some or all of their initial investment and therefore no money should be invested that users cannot afford to lose.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">As with any market, for a transaction to happen it requires a seller, a buyer, and a price agreement. Loss-limiting strategies such as stop-loss orders may not be effective because market conditions or technological issues may make it impossible to execute stop-loss orders. {{ get_settings('website_name')}} is not responsible for any losses incurred as a result of using {{ get_settings('website_name')}}’s advisory services.</span></p><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">‍</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>7. Privacy</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} is fully compliant with GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation), an EU regulation enforceable as of May 25, 2018. {{ get_settings('website_name')}} stores the minimum possible amount of user data necessary to deliver its services. Stored user data includes: name, date of birth, country of residence, email address, and exchange API keys (encrypted). User data will never be shared with any third party before explicit user consent. Users have the right for their user data to be forgotten, which can be requested over email.</span></p><h3><span style="color: #f0f0f0;"><b>8. Communication</b></span></h3><p><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">The User understands and agrees to the preceding sections. The User also agrees to the following:</span></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">User agrees to not hold {{ get_settings('website_name')}} liable for any realized trading loss in any currency or asset;</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">User reserves the right to stop using {{ get_settings('website_name')}} at any point;</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">You agrees and warrants that any information provided to {{ get_settings('website_name')}} is accurate and complete;</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">User agrees that {{ get_settings('website_name')}} is offering a Software as a Service (SaaS). This means that {{ get_settings('website_name')}} monitors user accounts on users’ behalf on exchanges that are not affiliated with {{ get_settings('website_name')}};</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">User agrees to take full responsibility for identifying and paying any tax liabilities that may exist as a result of trading, or {{ get_settings('website_name')}} services in general;</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">This agreement is governed by and construed in accordance with the Dutch law and any dispute, which cannot be amicably resolved, shall be submitted to the jurisdiction of the Court in the Netherlands;</span></li><li aria-level="1"><span style="color: #f0f0f0;">{{ get_settings('website_name')}} reserves the right to terminate or deny service to anyone, at any time, for any reason.</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></article><p> </p></div></div></div><div class="elementor elementor-260 elementor-location-footer" data-elementor-type="footer" data-elementor-id="260"><section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f9b2b6d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="f9b2b6d" data-element_type="section" data-setting